                    )</title></titleStmt><sourceDesc><bibl type="frus-volume-id">frus1945v08</bibl><bibl type="frus-document-id">d402</bibl><bibl type="frus-document-number">402</bibl><bibl type="frus-div-subtype">historical-document</bibl></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><settingDesc><setting><date notBefore="1945-11-19T20:00:00-05:00" notAfter="1945-11-19T20:00:00-05:00"/></setting></settingDesc></profileDesc></teiHeader><text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1945-11-19T20:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1945-11-19T20:00:00-05:00" n="402" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d402">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">891.00/11–1945: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Iran</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Murray</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-11-19T20:00:00-05:00">November 19, 1945—8 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>634. For your information, Iranian situation is receiving prominent treatment in
                    press. UP reports that widespread revolution led by Democratic Party has broken
                    out in Azerbaijan; that Russian trucks are distributing weapons to rebels; that
                    insurgents have captured Ahar, Sarab, Maragheh, Mianeh and surrounded garrisons
                    in Tabriz, Ardebil, Rezaiyeh, Astara; that insurgents are marching on
                    Tehran.</p>
                <p>Dept is awaiting your report and would appreciate information concerning measures
                    if any which Iranian Govt has taken or contemplates.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Byrnes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
